  "text": {
    "en": {
      "name": "Jurrac Astero",
      "effect": "1 Tuner + 1+ non-Tuner Dinosaur monsters\nIf this card is Synchro Summoned: You can Set 1 \"Jurrac\" Spell/Trap from your Deck or GY. Once per turn, when your opponent would Special Summon a monster(s) (Quick Effect): You can banish 2 Dinosaur monsters from your GY; negate the Summon, and if you do, destroy that monster(s). During your opponent's turn (Quick Effect): You can banish 2 \"Jurrac\" monsters from your GY, including this card; Special Summon 1 \"Jurrac Meteor\" from your Extra Deck. (This is treated as a Synchro Summon.)",
      "official": false
    },
    "ja": {
